   "source": [
    "## Step 4: Summarize the long term trends\n",
    "\n",
    "### 4a) Comparing historical and projected number of days in each year above a Heat Index threshold\n",
    "\n",
    "Using the OSHA thresholds we noted above, we'll now look at a threshold of 95°F. Again, we **strongly recommend** looking at multiple thresholds to understand Heat Index trends."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 29,
   "id": "94cd68f1-15ed-49da-9ee9-f363016b8d17",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "hi_threshold = 95  # degF"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "eb4ce6ae-0afd-4d97-bb9f-dc9e0ceb36a5",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
